      <script>TIMEOUT(1000); /* 3600 seconds or 1 hour */

log.log("Starting COOJA logger\n");

timeout_function = function () {
    log.log("Script timed out.\n");
    log.testOK();
}

while (true) {
    if (msg) {

    YIELD();
}</script>
